  "abstract": "<jats:p>The main aspects of obtaining artificial ceramic binders (ACB) based on aluminosilicate raw materials are considered. Their rheological properties and dispersion composition are analyzed. A comparative analysis of the technological properties of ACB obtained by different methods is carried out. The optimal method for obtaining ACB is identified and the possibility of using them as matrix systems for the manufacture of refractory composite materials for various purposes is established. Ill. 3. Ref. 6. Tab. 4.</jats:p>",
